      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented in FDA benchmark dataset. Flow rates and rotational speeds match simulation boundary conditions within measurement uncertainty. Temperature and fluid viscosity controlled and reported."
