    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable under ASME V&V 40 at Model Risk Level 2. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion confirmed across all 5 flow-speed combinations evaluated.",
